    "name": "Crypto Mining",
    "steam_appid": 3225300,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225300/extras/17485f3b019f984ed36f79a7e4943dd6.avif?t=1761985911\" width=800 height=100 /></span><strong>加密挖掘是一个引人入胜的模拟器，你成为一名矿工，并建立自己的&quot;加密帝国&quot;。&quot; </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理加密货币挖掘，优化空间，购买设备和分析市场。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>承担风险，扩展您的业务，并证明您是加密货币世界的大师！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225300/extras/30f1cfc2ec05f0e30edb4936a3032943.avif?t=1761985911\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在线市场上直接从制造商处订购产品，以获得更好的性能。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225300/extras/a2fe264ff1ac774ed8531fd47a92e7c3.avif?t=1761985911\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>购买市场上的产品，如果你想省钱，但也得到更差的性能。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225300/extras/130437331bfca0732e5c385755eebd2c.avif?t=1761985911\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>对于赌博，PC上有一个赌场，它有这样的模式：21点，骰子。我们祝您成功赢得世界上所有的钱！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225300/extras/b3fbc99bbbcc67f615e053c81f2e0e6c.avif?t=1761985911\" width=800 height=100 /></span><strong>交易大型加密货币巨头，如：NETCOIN，ETH，BTC。密切关注价格图表，并在盈利时退出交易，只为你！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225300/extras/16e84d054bd39e8e0f07777f126553e1.avif?t=1761985911\" width=800 height=100 /></span>感觉像一个成年人，因为你将不得不支付账单，或者更确切地说，罚款，非法采矿，盗窃货物，以及电力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225300/extras/b4192372c9b946e9f93f4884371f8429.avif?t=1761985911\" width=800 height=100 /></span>根据您的颜色和口味构建钻机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超频你的显卡，以获得你的GPU的最佳性能！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>即将推出的功能:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-VR！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-新内容！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-在线模式！</strong></p>",
